    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>Gene Zentko is a Florida-based sales executive with more than 15 years of experience in healthcare and animal health sales, spanning laboratory diagnostics, medical devices, and veterinary diagnostics. Alongside his sales career, Gene owns and operates several Florida-based digital businesses.</p>

    <h2>Career background</h2>
    <p>Gene's career has centered on diagnostic and healthcare sales — working with clinical laboratories, diagnostic testing companies, and animal health organizations on territory management, business development, and long-term account relationships with healthcare providers and veterinary practices across Florida.</p>

    <h2>Entrepreneurship</h2>
    <p>Outside of his sales career, Gene founded and operates three Florida-based businesses:</p>
    <div class="ventures">
      <div class="venture-card">
        <strong>Florida Buzz</strong> — a Florida travel and lifestyle publication covering theme parks, beaches, and local news.
        <br><a href="https://thefloridabuzz.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">thefloridabuzz.com</a>
      </div>
      <div class="venture-card">
        <strong>Villages Golf Cart Trader</strong> — a free local golf cart marketplace serving The Villages, FL and surrounding communities.
        <br><a href="https://villagesgolfcarttrader.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">villagesgolfcarttrader.com</a>
      </div>
      <div class="venture-card">
        <strong>Cartzilla</strong> — a golf cart parts and accessories store built on hands-on industry experience.
        <br><a href="https://cartzillagolfcart.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">cartzillagolfcart.com</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Based in Florida</h2>
    <p>Gene lives in the Central Florida area, in and around The Villages, where his hands-on interest in golf cart mechanical and electrical work directly informs his work with Villages Golf Cart Trader and Cartzilla.</p>

